@startuml
title UC-07 Grade Assignment (Sequence)
participant Instructor
participant WebApp
participant AssignmentService
participant DB
participant NotificationService
participant User

Instructor -> WebApp: open submission
WebApp -> AssignmentService: getSubmission(submissionId)
AssignmentService -> DB: SELECT submission
DB --> AssignmentService: submission data
AssignmentService --> WebApp: show submission
Instructor -> WebApp: enter grade & feedback -> submit
WebApp -> AssignmentService: gradeSubmission(submissionId, grade, feedback, graderId)
AssignmentService -> DB: UPDATE submission (grade, status=GRADED)
DB --> AssignmentService: updated
AssignmentService -> NotificationService: notifyStudent(studentId, grade)
NotificationService --> User: in-app/email
AssignmentService --> WebApp: result
WebApp --> Instructor: confirmation
@enduml
